## @file
#  Dxe driver that dynamically creates and publishes the HEST table.
#
#  This driver creates HEST header and provides protocol service to add
#  and install the HEST table.
#  This driver creates HEST header adds HEST error source descriptors and
#  publishes the table to OS.
